208
00:27:37,920 --> 00:27:39,555
And you...

209
00:27:40,503 --> 00:27:42,255
You are powerful and rich.

210
00:27:43,662 --> 00:27:45,192
You own all this land

211
00:27:46,162 --> 00:27:48,038
And you love me.

212
00:27:49,554 --> 00:27:50,766
