217
00:28:09,340 --> 00:28:11,314
We must be born under
the same star.

218
00:28:11,440 --> 00:28:13,383
Don't talk about the stars.

219
00:28:14,180 --> 00:28:15,247
Why not?

220
00:28:17,014 --> 00:28:20,678
