251
00:30:19,253 --> 00:30:20,316
Aha, yes

252
00:30:20,643 --> 00:30:22,888
And you didn't notice anything
yesterday at the castle ?

253
00:30:22,920 --> 00:30:29,841
She and the young knight,their eyes were 
